{"updated_at": "2012-11-08T04:58:33Z", "repo": "rails", "created_at": "2012-11-08T04:58:33Z", "owner": "rails", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/10176908", "id": 10176908, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/3096", "issue_id": 3096, "user": {"repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/lighttroupe/repos", "type": "User", "html_url": "https://github.com/lighttroupe", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/lighttroupe/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/lighttroupe/subscriptions", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/lighttroupe/following{/other_user}", "gravatar_id": "b3846998590d062b03b80f1494db93e0", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/lighttroupe/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/lighttroupe", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/lighttroupe/gists{/gist_id}", "avatar_url": "https://1.gravatar.com/avatar/b3846998590d062b03b80f1494db93e0?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F64deac9b86883f90d9557991ff06abef.png", "id": 1422772, "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/lighttroupe/events{/privacy}", "login": "lighttroupe", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/lighttroupe/received_events", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/lighttroupe/followers"}, "body": "I'm seeing the ActionView::Template::Error (\"File name too long\") exception on Ubuntu 12.04 with Rails 3.2.8.\r\n\r\nThe assumption that the file system can handle 255 character file names doesn't hold when using eCryptfs, which is common: it's used by Ubuntu's one-click install-time \"encrypt my home directory\" feature.\r\n\r\n> So we (as eCryptfs upstream developers) typically recommend you limit your filenames to ~140 characters.\r\n\r\nhttp://unix.stackexchange.com/questions/32795/what-is-the-maximum-allowed-filename-and-folder-size-with-ecryptfs\r\n\r\nThis works for me:\r\nActiveSupport::Cache::FileStore::FILENAME_MAX_SIZE = 115", "_id": {"$oid": "52383ad2bd3543c15101020a"}, "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/3096#issuecomment-10176908"}
